overview: "This Kodachrome color film was shot in Kinsale and its surroundings, in Ireland in 2013. An Irish summer glimpse : sand castle contest, children-fairies dancing, a fake Katy Perry concert. It was developed in 2017 with D94 & D95 revealers in Mire Lab, Nantes, France." (the8fest)
title: Kinsale, Eire
